ActEnterprise Cape Breton Corporation Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister for the purposes of the Atlantic Canada Opportunities Agency Act of EVA JUNE (MAUGER) LANDRY of St. Peter's, Nova Scotia, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Enterprise Cape Breton Corporation to hold office for a term of three years, in the place of Sonny MacDougall.
